Buy the new Sony MSMT16G 16GB Memory Stick PRO Duo (Mark2) Media:                                                                      &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.amazon.com/Sony-MSMT16G-Memory-Stick-Mark2/dp/B0013AX2HO/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.amazon.com/Sony-MSMT16G-Memory-Stick-Mark2/dp/B0013AX2HO/&lt;/a&gt;

